title: From Beyond
overview: Do you believe in the the "beyond"?AJ Barrera is about to stretch the limits of what you consider reality. In the reality TV series From Beyond, the young psychic medium will take viewers as he tracks down paranormal activity in Southland Latino communities.The ghost hunter teams up with paranormal investigators Christian Vera and Ramiro Ramirez to uncover the unique relationship Latinos have with the the "beyond".
